## 🌐 **Service Ports & Design Principles**
**Ports**: Phoenix:4000, PostgreSQL:5433, MinIO:9000, Jellyfish:5002, Prometheus:9568, SIA DC-09:3061
**Principles**: Multi-tenancy first, event-driven real-time, distributed PG2 scaling, security default, compliance ready, Elixir-native, performance optimized

## 🌐 **Service Ports**

| Service | Port | Purpose |
|---------|------|----------|
| Phoenix | 4000 | Main web application |
| PostgreSQL | 5433 | Database (dev) |
| MinIO | 9000 | S3-compatible storage |
| Jellyfish | 5002 | WebRTC media server |
| Prometheus | 9568 | Metrics collection |
| SIA DC-09 | 3061 | Alarm panel protocol |

## 🏗️ **Key Design Principles**

1.0 - **Multi-Tenancy First** - Complete isolation by design
2.0 - **Event-Driven** - Real-time with backpressure handling
